{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they will say, there are the prisoner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They are very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They're singing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then, they knew that-- they knew that we were Italians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they invariably, every day they want us to sing 'Mama,' because it was a song that has come in, you know, in vogue at this very moment.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then, they liked that song.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they want us to sing every morning when we're carrying these bricks-- very, very heavy-- to the place what they were, you know, designated-- and to sing 'Mama.' We had not even strength to walk, never mind to sing.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But we were doing all the same.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next day, now, we were ordered to take squares of lawn-- very, very happy-- to be-- carry the same place where we have, the previous day-- we have putted the bricks.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were carrying those pieces of lawn to that place where the bricks were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, bring it back-- those bricks that we have taken the day before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was really no sense what we were doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's just, you know, to make us weak, and demoralized, and thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were, you know, doing those things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, we were-- already know, at night, you know, they were giving us a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the-- the-- the-- as we were-- you know, again, at night, we were also counted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were counted in the morning at 8 o'clock, and in the evening at 6 o'clock-- in very-- every day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So from 5 o'clock, we have to be in the-- in the queues again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The German will count if it were all the same, you know, number.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
